episodes.title: JW Jehovah's Witnesses EXPOSED!!! My personal experience with JW's
episodes.description:
SUBSCRIBE and SHARE!
This Vlog is my personal experience growing up as one of Jehovah's Witnesses and how I came to be disfellowshipped/disassociated. Also, the psychological effect that the cult's shunning doctrine had on me. If you have had a similar experience, please share! And speak out! You are not alone.
The links I mentioned are here:

https://www.youtube.com/user/johncedars1929

www.jwsurvey.org

Thank you for watching! : Please SUBSCRIBE and SHARE.
